OL,3,CUnited Utilities top bosses have
OL,4,Cbonuses blocked
OL,6,FUnited Utilities is among six other
OL,7,Fmajor water suppliers to have blocked
OL,8,Fbonus payouts to its top bosses over
OL,9,Fserious pollution incidents and
OL,10,Fvarious performance issues.
OL,12,FWater regulator Ofwat has said more
OL,13,Fthan #4million of potential bonuses
OL,14,Fwere banned under new rules on
OL,15,Fperformance-related executive pay.
OL,17,FThe powers were introduced in June as
OL,18,Fa result of concerns that the pay of
OL,19,Fwater firms' top bosses was not
OL,20,Freflecting their environmental
OL,21,Fperformance.
