OL,3,CUnited Utilities top bosses have
OL,4,Cbonuses blocked
OL,6,FIt means companies are required to
OL,7,Fblock annual bonuses and other awards
OL,8,Fto directors where they do not comply
OL,9,Fwith the watchdog's rules.
OL,11,FThis includes pollution incidents,
OL,12,Fpoor environmental practices and
OL,13,Fcriminal convictions.
OL,15,FThe six companies, ` United Utilities
OL,16,FWater, Anglian Water, Southern Water,
OL,17,FThames Water, Wessex Water and
OL,18,FYorkshire Water ` blocked payouts for
OL,19,Fa variety of failures, mostly
OL,20,Finvolving pollution.
