OL,3,CUnited Utilities top bosses have
OL,4,Cbonuses blocked
OL,6,FOfwat also said it was planning to
OL,7,Fchange the rules around water
OL,8,Fcompanies' annual reporting so that
OL,9,Fthey must publicly share details of
OL,10,Fpay received by directors from the
OL,11,Fregulated, group and parent firms.
