OL,3,CUnited Utilities top bosses have
OL,4,Cbonuses blocked
OL,6,FOfwat wrote in its report: "More
OL,7,Fbroadly, while there has been some
OL,8,Fprogress in certain areas on
OL,9,Faccountability, water companies must
OL,10,Fbetter demonstrate that they
OL,11,Funderstand the feeling of public anger
OL,12,Fon bonuses and the expectation that
OL,13,Fthey are accountable, and reflect this
OL,14,Fbetter in their decisions on executive
OL,15,Fremuneration."
OL,17,FOfwat said that a further #2.4million
OL,18,Fof performance-related executive pay
OL,19,Fwas not required to be blocked, but
OL,20,Fshould not be funded by customers.
