OL,3,CUnited Utilities top bosses have
OL,4,Cbonuses blocked
OL,6,FAmong the firms that triggered its
OL,7,Frules, Thames Water had seven
OL,8,F"category 1" pollution incidents,
OL,9,Fwhich are the most serious, recorded
OL,10,Fin 2024.
OL,12,FIt also breached its licence to hold a
OL,13,Fsufficient credit rating and had a one-
OL,14,Fstar rating in relation to its
OL,15,Fenvironmental performance.
OL,17,FThis meant that no bonuses or other
OL,18,Fawards were paid to its chief
OL,19,Fexecutive or its former finance chief,
OL,20,Fwho left in March.
