OL,3,CUnited Utilities top bosses have
OL,4,Cbonuses blocked
OL,6,FWessex Water triggered Ofwat's rule
OL,7,Fdue to a criminal conviction for a
OL,8,Fsewage leak last year which killed
OL,9,Fmore than 2,000 fish and resulted in a
OL,10,F#500,000 fine.
OL,12,FThe company said it therefore decided
OL,13,Fnot to pay any executive bonuses.
